	<Language_en_US>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_CREATIVE_EXPRESSION_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>The Importance of Being Earnest</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_CREATIVE_EXPRESSION_HELP">
			<Text>Your openness with your people has prompted what might be considered... outbursts from figures in our entertainment industries and educational institutions.[NEWLINE]How shall we proceed?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_CREATIVE_EXPRESSION_HELP_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>Put up with 1 [ICON_HAPPINESS_4] Unhappiness in each City so that whenever a Policy is adopted you receive [ICON_CULTURE] Culture in every City.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_CREATIVE_EXPRESSION_HELP_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>Your [ICON_GREAT_WRITER] Writers each generate +2 [ICON_GOLD] Gold and +2 [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_CREATIVE_EXPRESSION_HELP_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>Invest {1_YieldCost} in societal participation projects so that during [ICON_GOLDEN_AGE] Golden Ages your Cities produce +10% [ICON_CULTURE] Culture.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_CREATIVE_EXPRESSION_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>These mild discontents now shall all be forgiven when our plans come to fruition. We have no need to threaten or oppress, a free and open society necessarily involves conversations such as these.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_CREATIVE_EXPRESSION_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>These shows that are being produced to ridicule us are really rather funny. It is ironic, perhaps, that allowing a free public discourse should be able to - in some small way - bolster the economy.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_CREATIVE_EXPRESSION_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>A little back and forth is all very well and good, but I am somewhat concerned with the direction of this. We need to make sure that people are not becoming dangerously disaffected with the state.</Text>
		</Row>

